		</ingredient>
	</ingredients>
	<preparation>In a saucepan, mix water, sugar, cocoa and salt.  Bring to a boil and stir at boil for two minutes.  Stir in milk and bring to heat but do not boil.

Mix in vanilla and serve.</preparation>
